revision.text:
{{Documentation subpage}}
{{High-use}}

This template generates a line containing the page type, the last editor of the page, a link to the [[Help:Diff|diff]] for the edit, and the approximate amount of time since the edit (provided by {{tl|Time ago}}).

=== Usage ===
* <code><nowiki>{{last edited by}}</nowiki></code>
renders as
* {{last edited by}}
while
* <code><nowiki>{{last edited by|brief=yes}}</nowiki></code>

renders as
* {{last edited by|brief=yes}}

=== See also ===
*[[Help:Magic words]]
*{{tl|REVISIONUSER}}
*{{tl|REVISIONUSER2}}
*{{tl|REVISIONTIMESTAMP}}

